data.description: GREAT location right in town in this 4 unit complex. Well laid out floor plans with good sized kitchen/eating area and two nice sized bedrooms. Air Base road, restaurants, movie theater and shopping close by. Brand new roof 2023, 2 units with newer water heaters. Owner owned washer/dryer, refrigerators & above the range microwaves in each unit. Own covered parking and a few uncovered spots for guests. All units have central air and forced gas HVAC. Solid rent history.
